value.0: Smooth and exotic silk sheets line this mattress which is stuffed with some material that feels as if your sleeping on a cloud. Top qualty wool and cotton comforters, washed to a point that they feel extremely soft, with satiny smooth pillows for a perfect head rest, complete this package. Resting here would be akin to a blessing from the gods.

This bed has a beaten straw mattress, lined with well worn cotton sheets and covered with a worn woolen blanket.  Tended quite well, washed and scented, you will not find any bedbugs living here.  Soft enough to allow even the most hard adventurer a decent nights rest.
